Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:49.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}曖昧な線　揺曳な隙まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:55.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}無邪気なあざとさで夢を繋いだの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.36,0:22:59.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}噓だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:02.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:07.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}純度だけは固くて
